| Plot                    = Bitten by a radioactive spider in the subway, Brooklyn teenager [[Miles Morales (Earth-1610B)|Miles Morales]] suddenly develops mysterious powers that transform him into the one and only Spider-Man. When he meets [[Peter Parker (Earth-616B)|Peter Parker]], he soon realizes that there are many others who share his special, high-flying talents. Miles must now use his newfound skills to battle the evil [[Wilson Fisk (Earth-1610B)|Kingpin]], a hulking madman who can open portals to other universes and pull different versions of [[Spider-Man]] into our world.

